    "### Baye's Theorem\n",
    "* **P (A | B) = P (B | A) * P(A) / P(B)**\n",
    "\n",
    "### If we had Target (y) and Feature (X) variables... \n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "* **P (y | X) = P (X | y) * P(y) / P(X)**\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "### If I have more than one X, (X1, X2, X3)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "* **P (X | y) = P(X1 | y) * P(X2 | y) * P(X3 | y)**\n",
    "    - Baye's Theorem\n",
    "        - **P (y | X) = P(X1 | y) * P(X2 | y) * P(X3 | y) * P(y) / P(X1) * P(X2) * P(X3)**"
